description:
Darkness Radio presents Supernatural News/Parashare: 22 Of The Spookiest Stories Ever Edition!

It certainly has been a strange and supernatural week of NEWS stories, but Tim and Bruiser have a little surprise for you this week as well! 

This week, Hi-Res photos from the 70's (isn't that an oxymoron?) clearly show a flying saucer in earth's atmosphere! We hear the sound of a giant black hole in space! And this week, we feature 20 plus stories that will send a chill down your spine!
